pov: everything is a core memory 🥹🫶🏼🤍✨
aquaholic💧

From moving across the country, traveling to 4 countries, making new friends, dealing with heartbreak, learning new things, experiencing life lessons, moving back home to Hawai‘i… this has been one of the craziest years I’ve ever had. All I can say is ✨MAHALO 2022✨ for allowing me to make my own decisions & challenging me to be outside of my comfort zone. I can’t wait to see what life will throw at me next… let’s bring on the new year!

happy birthday to my favorite egg 🪺🤍
i get butterflies when i look into your eyes 🎶🦋

a month ago, i felt so out of place. i missed being in Hilo with my friends and was so scared that I had just moved to a new city all alone to start a new job. it’s only been one month and today, i feel so at peace with the decision that I made to live here. becoming friends with people from my hometown, meeting people through social media, and just random girls coming up to me at the beach to be friends *cough* @preeyapprasad *cough* has made me realize that when one door closes, many more will open. big decisions may be uncomfortable at first, but it’s only gonna help you grow within yourself and things always get better with time. 

life has been real vibey lately 🧚🏼‍♀️🪄✨📸
